    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person to believe it. Honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied this car\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, professionally detailed, and treated like a member of the family. It drives like an absolute dream and is in truly flawless condition. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm excited for it to find a great new home. Drop me a message if you want to take a look!",
