    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically impeccable: the critical rod bearing service and double-VANOS system overhaul have been performed to ensure long-term reliability. The chassis is reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points, preserving factory torsional rigidity. Power is managed via a crisp ZF 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. With zero deferred maintenance and a pristine underside, this vehicle delivers the precise, communicative handling and linear power delivery that defined an era of motorsport.",
      "price": 46500.0,
