    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in breathtaking showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with absolutely zero chips, scratches, or imperfections, while the factory alloy wheels remain untouched and curb-rash free. Inside, the cabin is a masterclass in preservation; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any bolster wear or creasing, and the dashboard remains pristine under consistent UV protection. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system, functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, providing a smooth, silent ride that feels identical to its first day on the road. Accompanied by a full, documented service history and a spotless engine bay, this is undoubtedly the finest example available for a discerning collector or enthusiast.",
      "price": 46500.0,
